angular basics -> 2022

-----------
$ npx -p @angular/cli ng new proj-name --style=scss
-----------

generator -> @angular/cli
	2 mins required to created angular app
	
	Install @angular/cli
		- install npm by installing node
			- download and install nodejs
			- node -v (14 =+ is required)
			- npm -v
			
		- npm install -g @angular/cli
		
			only for virtual machines
			C:\Users\123\AppData\Roaming\npm
				add this path to PATH environment variable 
				C:\Users\123\AppData\Roaming\npm
		- ng version
		- Create angular project
		- ng new project-name
		
		
Structure -> 
	open/flexible
	
	
	angular.json
	tsconfig
	karma
	
	package.json==pom.xml
	
		src/index.html
		src/main.ts
			import AppModule from ......
			
			
			buttons
			header
			login
			chart
			modules
				user
					profile
					welcome
			services
				user.service.ts
				emp.service.ts
			
			
-----------------
Start app: npm run start

	localhost:4200

Stop app: ctrl + c

readme.md
	ng g ... name
	
		c component
		s service
		g guard
		m module
		
		
change port: 
	package.json
		start: "ng serve --port 3000"



